title: Cozy Home West Of Brickell
posting_body: ['Freshly renovated 3/1 house with new appliances in minutes from Brickell.', 'The house is located in a safe and quiet neighborhood, surrounded by beautiful historical homes...4 minute drive to Brickell, Downtown, walking distance to Calle 8 walk of fame, 12 minute drive to the beach and MIA airport.', 'There are plenty of great restaurants and things to do in the area such as tours, historical monuments, museums, shopping, nightlife and entertainment.', 'The house is a completely gut renovated 3 bedroom/1 bathroom standalone duplex.', 'Tenant is responsible for most utilities including lawn maintenance.', 'Tenant is not allowed to rent any or all part of the property via any home sharing sites, such as, but not limited to, Airbnb, Vrbo, HomeAway, etc. Must complete our background/credit check and be able to verify income.', 'Owner pays water;', 'Tenant pays electricity;', "Last month's rent due at signing;", 'Pet fee can apply;', 'No smoking inside the house.', '*serious inquiries only*']
